{"tid":1558014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 用Android嘅入黎幫手試求救app","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T05:33:39.000Z","uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74f5f3d219076e220ef99e084a63921d5f5f4acd","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"用Apple就話有Paracute啫 用Andoid嘅幫手試下呢個app<br />\n佢可以做到<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">好L多function</span></strong> (eg. send個msg俾自已叫部電話響/ 叫朋友send個msg俾自已check 下部機嘅位置 或者<span style=\"color: blue;\">開始錄音</span>....) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日share呢個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">求救SMS</span></strong>出黎 各位用Android機嘅幫手睇下好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單黎講, 開左以下嘅flow 之後, <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>唔駛解鎖 long press volume up </strong></span>就可以send到一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有location嘅SOS msg</span></strong><br />\n1. Download 呢個app 然後安左佢 <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.llamalab.automate&amp;hl=zh_TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.llamalab.automate%26hl%3Dzh_TW&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=fca18363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.llamalab.automate&amp;hl=zh_TW</a><br />\n2. 開左app之後click 右上角有三個人嘅icon 再search &quot;<strong>Vol up SOS</strong>&quot;<br />\n3. Download flow 之後返去home page 會見到 click 入去start flow<br />\n4. First run 會問你<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">拎permission</span></strong>. 呢個flow要求<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">四樣野</span></strong><br />\n     - access screen content and observe your actions<br />\n     - send and view SMS messages<br />\n     - access precise ocation (GPS and netrowk-based)<br />\n     - read phone status and identity<br />\n5. Grant all 之後可以開始, 跟住入面的提示, 入哂資料就用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f3e51e74d1dd39ff5c0365562cdeb3b4c07c03","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">留意返</span></ins></strong><br />\n- long press 到震可以鬆手 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">再震即係send 左</span></strong> <strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"> 唔會有通知</span></strong>但係你個msg app 會睇到<br />\n- 目前係有location name + coordinates <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>萬一GPS唔work 會照send</strong></span>但location 係N/A<br />\n- 唔用隨時stop flow 就得<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Send msg 係要錢架 係要錢架 係要錢架</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試過入基本資料加位置要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2個</span></strong>開始計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- Run 緊會<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">disable 左個 vol up</span></strong>, 可以係Key Pressed -&gt; Key Codes 一格自己揀另一個制<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">唔駛解鎖</span>但係要screen on</strong> (ambient display都得)"},{"pid":"28520455fbb47b2ea13b407292df6c452aff0feb","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"<ins>關於呢個app </ins><br />\n* No root needed, 但係root 左可以run 到多D function<br />\n* <span style=\"color: red;\">同時間run 30個block或以下係免費 </span><br />\n真心推大家試玩下其他function, 又或者你覺得上面呢個太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 試下<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">自己郁手改到啱你自己用</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOfficial website <a href=\"https://llamalab.com/automate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fllamalab.com%2Fautomate%2F&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=8b8629b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://llamalab.com/automate/</a><br />\nApp documentation (說明書) <a href=\"https://llamalab.com/automate/doc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fllamalab.com%2Fautomate%2Fdoc%2Findex.html&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=9d3843ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://llamalab.com/automate/doc/index.html</a><br />\nPrivacy policy <a href=\"https://llamalab.com/automate/doc/privacy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fllamalab.com%2Fautomate%2Fdoc%2Fprivacy.html&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=040a2673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://llamalab.com/automate/doc/privacy.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b3e7c09730d59c4d5588383b0b3e8940928681e","tid":1558014,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9.15 民陣遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年9月15日（日）<br />\n時間：下午 3:00 起步<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n遊行路線：從銅鑼灣東角道起步，遊行至遮打道行人專用區"},{"pid":"aacab1ca24ee05921e6497de22ea1337c070c40d","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"自推1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe63c3048e354d35d3b6047f16e73fe7252bc2be","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc86bef190e1364031b9bb1ec4838d4932d4bf25","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30d244caf9448fa263809d3260d85d9f226c5c0","tid":1558014,"uid":300500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"a1d8b758e3f254c0d1b1e564258eb67a81d62edc","t